Package: ghmapper
Title: Consume Routing Data from Graphhopper Routing API
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: person("Timo", "Roest", email = "timo.roest@me.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package allows someone to send routing
    requests to the Graph Hopper API, and quickly plot the
    various outcomes for visual inspection. Currently, the
    only algorithm implemented is that of the alternative
    routes. This package is initially used for debugging.
Depends: R (>= 3.5.1)
License: GNU GPLv3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports:
    jsonlite,
    leaflet,
    httr,
    sp,
    maptools,
    tibble,
    magrittr,
    purrr
RoxygenNote: 6.1.0.9000
Suggests: knitr,
    rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr
